{"tid":1401421,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"記住：我地依家追求緊五大訴求","createTime":"2019-08-03T14:45:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T15:18:23.000Z","uid":69901,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"51b0eb8100354a25c557a1da7345c68463a7d562","tid":1401421,"uid":69901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:45:27.000Z","msg":"重申5大訴求<br />\n<br />\n1. 撤回《逃犯條例》修訂；<br />\n2. 撤回暴動定性；<br />\n3. 撤銷所有抗爭者控罪，不可秋後算帳；<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會，調查警察濫暴濫權、追究警察開槍責任及元朗警黑勾結；<br />\n5. 全面落實雙普選。<br />\n<br />\n記住我地係要求緊呢5點，唔好唔好 比 個 人 情 緒 控 制 。 <br />\n<br />\n係呢5點凝聚左大家出來，要記住呢5點。達成呢5點，大家先再諗其他香港問題點算。<br />\n<br />\n我明白大家都抑壓左好耐，大家共同誰退。<br />\n<br />\n要對付警察的係獨立調查委員會呀！"},{"pid":"5b6056507a7bbad49cafa1fc110479a905be4ff8","tid":1401421,"uid":25169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:45:52.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[建議]關於罷買！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1401281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1401281</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7957a92e2079fcfc651d77ffcb38681ee2edd037","tid":1401421,"uid":283504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:45:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撤呀！全部人撤呀！我要8月5號見到你地！</span></span>"},{"pid":"396da0c3520ec0d10b96f32fb8fe12b108257cb3","tid":1401421,"uid":240902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:46:57.000Z","msg":"前線 Be water PLEASE，唔該，求求你地，唔好送人頭喇。我地8.5 需要人架"},{"pid":"32997c9687609cddfad681c6f07a7669a8dfaf0b","tid":1401421,"uid":241244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:47:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5f63f87d1eb00ba51804b730aee98b79ac1579e9","tid":1401421,"uid":42542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:47:29.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n只是五大訴求<br />\n不是不支持港獨，但不要失焦，請聚焦響大部份人都支持嘅議題"},{"pid":"ecc9e31aa6f6755540d1f7336a53669b27c85fa8","tid":1401421,"uid":69901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:02:10.000Z","msg":"每做一個決定前，都要諗下自己做緊既野係咪爲左5大訴求！"},{"pid":"c1b9fbd998ce55dacc919ef67ef818059f2408a5","tid":1401421,"uid":124618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qj6bzUZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQj6bzUZ.png&h=486f682e&s={SIZE}\" />不分化 不割席 不篤灰"},{"pid":"8a533a43244782115529bd4bf7fd949f7d064bb8","tid":1401421,"uid":124618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:18:23.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割席 不篤灰<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fKKAg82.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfKKAg82.png&h=3175aa43&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}